ww.theverge.com/24265074/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sale-tech-staff-picks-favorites-october-2024&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div >; &lt;p id=&quot;1dZhWj&quot;>;下面，我们精选了一些我们可以亲自担保的低于 50 美元的商品。当然，它们包括许多亚马逊自己的设备，包括 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/all-new-amazon-fire-tv-stick-4k-max/dp/B0BP9SNVH9?tag=theverge02 -20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Fire TV Stick 4K Max&lt;/a>;，最新&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Echo-Spot-TP-Link -Smart-Color/dp/B0DF15V76B?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Echo Spot&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com /Amazon-smart-plug-works-with-Alexa/dp/B089DR29T6?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊便宜的智能插头&lt;/a>;。我们的非亚马逊设备上还有很多值得注意的优惠...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24262440/amazon-prime-day-best- Cheap-tech-deals-under-50-october-2024&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24262440/amazon-prime-day-best-cheap-tech-deals-under-50-october-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24262440/amazon-prime-day-best-cheap-tech-deals-under-50-october-2024</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-09T20:13:46-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-09T20:13:46-04:00</updated><title>我们为亚马逊 Prime Day 找到的最佳笔记本电脑优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Asus Zenbook Duo 处于双屏模式。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/p48wWJ8xKtt46pJj947iWtVOhSw=/0x0:2700x1800/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73642810/246951_Asus_Zenbook_Duo_ABenedet to_0213.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;想象一下，获得这一切并在此过程中节省近 300 美元。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Antonio G. Di Benedetto / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;M4y5kP&quot;>;亚马逊并不以提供最优惠的笔记本电脑而闻名，但它的&lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.theverge.com/good-deals/24262468/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sales-tech-gadgets-october-2024&quot;>;正在进行的 Prime Big Deal Days 销售活动&lt;/a>;有一些实实在在的折扣 —如果考虑到&lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.me/cngroop5STO&quot;>;百思买的“48小时闪购”&lt;/a>;反计划，还有更多。如果您正在市场上购买新的 MacBook、Windows 生产力机器（包括新的 Copilot Plus PC），甚至是游戏笔记本电脑，我们会为您提供一些有价值的选择。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id= &quot;bnxbfQ&quot;>;虽然像百思买这样的专业电子零售商可能因日常笔记本电脑折扣而闻名，但亚马逊也有其公平的份额。如果您购买 MacBook，尤其如此，其中一些 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/8/24265354/apple-macbook-air-13-15-m3 -processor-october-prime-day-deal-sale&quot;>;亚马逊目前拥有迄今为止的最低价格&lt;/a>;。当然，您不会获得广泛的选择...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/2024/10/9/24262303 /amazon-prime-day-best-buy-sale-laptop-macbook-windows-gaming-deal&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/2024/10/9/24262303/amazon-prime-day-best-buy-sale-laptop-macbook-windows-gaming-deal" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/2024/10/9/24262303/amazon-prime-day-best-buy-sale-laptop-macbook-windows-gaming-deal</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-09T19:53:25-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-09T19:53:25-04:00</updated><title>我们发现的最佳 Prime Day 智能家居优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;飞利浦 Hue 的 Festavia 灯串挂在栅栏和圣诞树上。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/w4jOcAqy9nuBFTV-xbBEjwTVfrs=/0x63:1500x1063/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73639778/ph​​ilipshuefestavialights.5.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;飞利浦 Hue 的 Festavia 灯可用作万圣节装饰或在假期期间增添一点节日气氛。&lt;/em>; |图片：Philips Hue&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;fm1O1l&quot;>;亚马逊的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/17/24244180/amazon-october-prime- day-big-deal-days-fall-dates-2024&quot;>;Prime Big Deal Days&lt;/a>; 已进入第二天，与昨天的情况一样，这仍然是在 Great smart 上购买优惠的绝佳时机家用装备。我们搜索了&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22954554/best-video-doorbell-camera&quo