me-desk-logitech-sony&quot;>;&lt;em>;David Pierce，特约编辑&lt;/ em>;&lt;/a>;&lt;/h3>; &lt;h2 id=&quot;a93TTt&quot;>;一把舒适的办公椅&lt;/h2>; &lt;div id=&quot;1Xny3W&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;productcard:12447883&quot;>;&lt;/ div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;pZpbuA&quot;>;我只需在亚马逊上查找该名称：它是“&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B06Y3PGPR2/?tag= theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;HON 办公椅黑色 |点火2.0 |符合人体工程学...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24265605/amazon-prime-day-deals-home-office-wfh-desk-accessories- sale-october-2024&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24265605/amazon-prime-day-deals-home-office-wfh-desk-accessories-sale-october-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24265605/amazon-prime-day-deals-home-office-wfh-desk-accessories-sale-october-2024</id><author><name>芭芭拉·克拉斯诺夫</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-09T18:47:52-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-09T18:47:52-04:00</updated><title>亚马逊 Prime Day 第二天您可以买到的最优惠商品</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Prime Day 期间提供的各种产品的图形照片拼贴。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/tm2JnOqRCfx0OYc9chLKchgFuso=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73638984/247273_Prime_Big_Deals_Days_2024_CV irginia_POST_EVENT_ROUNDUP.5.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;无论您是想要一副耳机、智能家居升级、充电器还是其他东西，仍然有时间节省各种技术完全不同。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/24262468/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sales-tech-gadgets-october-2024 &quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/24262468/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sales-tech-gadgets-october-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/24262468/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sales-tec